OL,3,CChild killer's parole hearing will not
OL,4,Cbe public following 'fresh allegations'
OL,6,FDouble child killer Colin Pitchfork's
OL,7,Fnext parole hearing will no longer be
OL,8,Fheld in public following "fresh
OL,9,Fallegations in respect of relatively
OL,10,Frecent conduct", The Parole Board has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe hearing was due to take place this
OL,14,Fweek but was adjourned and it will now
OL,15,Fbe relisted to be heard in private.
OL,17,FPitchfork was jailed for life in 1988
OL,18,Fafter raping and strangling 15-year-
OL,19,Fold girls Lynda Mann and Dawn Ashworth
OL,20,Fin Leicestershire in 1983 and 1986.
