OL,3,CChild killer's parole hearing will not
OL,4,Cbe public following 'fresh allegations'
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Parole Board
OL,7,Fsaid: "A panel of the Parole Board
OL,8,Fheld a directions hearing for Colin
OL,9,FPitchfork on Wednesday 10 July. At
OL,10,Fthat directions hearing the panel and
OL,11,Fboth parties discussed how best to
OL,12,Freceive evidence in respect of fresh
OL,13,Fallegations in the case. This included
OL,14,Fthe submission of new material to the
OL,15,Fpanel which relates to risk.
